== Meetings ==

Meetings are held on the 1st Sunday of each month at 9:00 PM on our team IRC channel, #ubuntu-us-az on libera.chat. Feel free to join us for some good conversation about upcoming events and Ubuntu related news. It's also a great time and place to introduce yourself if you are new to the group.
